Niue Documentation


	KNOWN BUGS


Niue sometimes has trouble with linebreaks in files
	
	To fix this, close Niue, open the file(s) that cause trouble with Pe,
	go to File->FileOptions and set 'Linebreaks' to Be/Unix.

Files are marked as 'unsaved' when you open a project

	Select the file(s).

Haiku: Mousewheel scrolling doesn't work

	No solution yet, this will be fixed after Haiku R1-alpha

